    <Folder>
      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The current military posture and activity patterns suggest a high level of operational tempo, with a focus on supporting Operation Epic Fury and regional security operations. The deployment of carrier strike groups, amphibious ready groups, and destroyers in the Pacific indicates a significant naval presence, while the presence of C-17 and A400 aircraft suggests ongoing transport and logistics operations. The overall assessment is that the US military is maintaining a high level of readiness and activity, with a focus on supporting ongoing operations and exercises. However, the depletion of Tomahawk cruise missile stocks and the strain on the tanker force are areas of concern that require attention. The situation in the Pacific remains dynamic, with the US military working to maintain a strong presence and support regional security operations.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
    </Folder>
